videoSnippet.title: Dangers of The Scotch || Ivanchuk vs Shahade || Chess.com Titled Tuesday (2020)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content and notifications https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Vassily Ivanchuk vs Greg Shahade
Titled Tuesday Chess.com (2020), 12.5.2020
Scotch, Goering gambit (C44)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 exd4 4. c3 dxc3 5. Nxc3 d6 6. Bc4 Nf6 7. Qb3 Qd7 8. Ng5 Ne5 9. Bb5 c6 10. f4 cxb5 11. fxe5 dxe5 12. Be3 h6 13. Rd1 Qe7 14. Qxb5+ Nd7 15. Nd5 Qd8 16. Qc4 hxg5 17. Nc7+ Ke7 18. O-O f6 19. Qe6
